reviewText: You are amazed at the human spirit to never give up!
a down to earth family story, with a wonderful love story to make it so much fun. We love Kang Jr Khan
There are lot of families loves and cares for each other and in the communities too. Very good scripting and acting. Good video quality.

The "Be Strong" series was a hit with my mother.  She loved the character particular showing how, under difficult circumstances, the heroin prevailed.  My mother wept and laughed with the character.  I wish the later sections of the series would be released in English.
